-- Barclays, Absa In Talks to Combine Their African Units
-- B y   K e i t h   C a m p b e l l
-- 2012-08-21T06:02:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-21/barclays-absa-in-talks-to-combine-their-african-units.html
Barclays Plc (BARC)  and  Absa Group Ltd. (ASA) 
said they are in talks to combine their African operations.
There is no certainty the talks will lead to a deal, the
companies said in a statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
